description: The investment objective of this Fund is to provide investors with a total return, taking into account both capital and income returns, which reflects the return of the ICE U.S. Treasury 7-10 Year Bond Index. In order to achieve its investment objective, the investment policy of this Fund is to invest in a portfolio of bonds that so far as possible and practicable consists of the component securities of the ICE U.S. Treasury 7-10 Year Bond Index, this Fund’s Benchmark Index.
name: iShares $ Treasury Bond 7-10yr UCITS ETF EUR Hedged (Dist)
